Fetch
=====

27-Jul-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
More readable formatting of byte sizes.

21-Jul-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Adding a password editing window.

18-Feb-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Support version 2 of the DownloadManager protocol.

10-Apr-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added extra buttons, which change.

17-Feb-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Re-enable the use of bytes_ready() to avoid blocking.

20-Jan-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~
Recognize application/octet-stream as a type servers return for an unknown 
type.  Better description of types.  Setting type when server disagrees now 
an option.  Moved option handling into options.py.

15-Dec-2006 (0.3.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use rox.basedir instead of rox.choices.
Can override waiting for DownloadManager to OK start.

06-Oct-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Can set the user.xdg.origin.url extended attribute on downloaded files.

29-Apr-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added i18n support.

11-Feb-2006 (0.3.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix problems relating to cancelling fetches.

16-Jan-2006
~~~~~~~~~~~
Increase maximum buffer size.
Added install section on options, to help those that are expecting it to
do something when run.

18-Dec-2005 (0.3.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Avoid deprecation warnings.

21-Nov-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Adapt for new DBUS interface.

20-Nov-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Fix deprecation warnings.

12-Nov-2005 (0.1.3, 0.2.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Update dclient.py from DownloadManager.
Added injector feed.

05-Nov-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added option to control update of window title.
Fix install instructions.

11-Sep-2005 (0.1.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Reduce redundant updates of the display and title (4* speed increase in my
connection slowed my desktop down!).

29-Jul-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Changed layout of window slightly.

15-May-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Switch to XDG choices.
Remove some dead code.  Extra error checks.  Track down stray ChildKill.

23-Apr-2005 (0.1.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Require ROX-Lib 2.0.0.
Use toplevel_ref() instead of main_loop().

14-Mar-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Standardized options (added app menu entry).  Shorter delays when connecting.
Updated dclient.py.

05-Mar-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Take care when filename has no '.' in it.

31-Jan-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use the signal sent by DownloadManager when a slot becomes available.

24-Jan-2005
~~~~~~~~~~~
Be compatible with pygtk 2.4.

04-Dec-2004 (0.1.0)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Use download manager.  Possible fix to stalled downloads (message
saying download finished stuck in pipe!).

22-Nov-2004 (0.0.6)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Error trap for the rename at end of fetch.

21-Nov-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Backend fetcher now just attempts to fetch a full buffer.  GUI can warn
if backend stalled.  Fetch to temporary file, renamed when fetch complete.
Added Bytes fetched to display.  Added comments on local and server type
not matching.

13-Nov-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Improvements to the file type icon display.

30-Oct-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Display the icon for the file type, if we can.

25-Sep-2004 (0.0.5)
~~~~~~~~~~~
More ways to avoid blocking reads.  Better report of partial download when 
cancelled.

21-Aug-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Split program into two processes: one to run the gui and the other to 
do the actual fetch.

05-Aug-2004 (0.0.4)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Better code for reading the socket, less chance of blocking.

26-Jun-2004 (0.0.3)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Option to set delay after download finished.  Fixed bug in password code.

20-Jun-2004 (0.0.2)
~~~~~~~~~~~
Added options (well, one so far).

19-Jun-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Prompt for and store passwords. Mark strings as translatable.

18-Jun-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Figure out type name when we start downloading.

12-Jun-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~
Expanded the display.  Start work towards password handling.

05-June-2004 (0.0.1)
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Let the URL label wrap to avoid the window becoming too wide.

02-June-2004
~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fixed update of progress bar.

-- 
$Id: Changes,v 1.41 2007/07/27 16:32:44 stephen Exp $
